name: HomePop_Navy_Chunky_Textured_Decorative_Storage_Bench_
reviews: I'm using the bench to cozy up a corner in my dressing room. I like it except for the brown wooden legs. Expresso would be better so I may stain/paint in the future.
This bench is really great for the price! The material looks great and the bench seems sturdy.

Love the quality of this storage bench. The woven fabric looks great and the wood legs are great quality. I had a bit of a struggle getting the screws in but did manage in the end. great piece, awesome value.
Sturdy, well made, clean lines - appearance as pictured.
Finally finished decorating my guest bedroom with this piece. Color is exactly as pictured. Great quality at a low price! Love it!
Perfect for what I needed - storage and bench. Nice looking.
